text.section:
To impose a benefit charge for the construction of a water supply or sewer system, the Commission shall classify each property that abuts on a street, road, lane, alley, right-of-way, or easement in which a water main or sewer line is to be laid as:
agricultural;
industrial or business;
institutional;
multiunit business;
multiunit residential;
residential subdivision; or
small acreage.
